    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2CbteVz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PZO90115</a></p>\r\n<p><b>Price</b> 100 gp; <b>Weight</b> 1 lb.</p>\r\n<p>This hollow clay container holds <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/weapons/weapon-descriptions/ammunition/black-powder\">black powder</a>, a <a class=\"spell\" href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/s/slow\">slow</a>-burning fuse, and rock salt or hard beads of resin or rubber. Lighting the fuse is a <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Move-Actions\">move action</a>; 1d3 rounds later, the sting grenade explodes, dealing 2d6 points of <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Nonlethal-Damage\">nonlethal damage</a> and 1d6 points of fire damage in a 10-foot-radius burst (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Reflex\">Reflex</a> DC 15 half). A sting grenade is treated as a <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Throw-Splash-Weapon\">splash weapon</a> with a range increment of 10 feet. Crafting this item requires a successful DC 25 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/craft\">Craft</a> (alchemy) check.</p>\r\n",
